Package at.tugraz.ist.ase.eval

Class Timer

java.lang.Object
at.tugraz.ist.ase.eval.AbstractEvaluator
at.tugraz.ist.ase.eval.Timer
public class Timer extends AbstractEvaluator
Simple class for measuring time in experiments. The timings of time measurements are stored in an array and can be retrieved using getTimings method.
